13:12.879 --> 13:15.142
OR WHAT,
YOU'LL HIT ME AGAIN?

13:15.185 --> 13:18.710
I'M ASKING YOU TO STAY,
WYLIE.

13:22.149 --> 13:23.106
OKAY.

13:23.150 --> 13:25.892
OKAY, GOOD.

13:25.935 --> 13:27.894
CHECK IN WITH TORK.

13:27.937 --> 13:29.243
I WANT TO KNOW WHAT'S GOING ON
AT THE HOUSE.

13:29.286 --> 13:30.287
SURE.

13:30.331 --> 13:32.507
AND CHO...

13:32.550 --> 13:35.031
THANKS.

13:35.075 --> 13:36.859
NO PROBLEM.

13:40.515 --> 13:43.126
THIS IS THE RING
WE SENT YOU A PICTURE OF.

13:43.170 --> 13:44.475
IT WAS MY GRANDMOTHER'S.

13:44.519 --> 13:46.303
ANNE'S DAD GAVE IT TO ME
TO PROPOSE WITH.

13:46.347 --> 13:49.263
WHICH IS SWEET, BUT IT'S NOT
REALLY ME, YOU KNOW?

13:49.306 --> 13:51.787
SO WE THOUGHT MAYBE WE COULD
TAKE THE DIAMOND OUT,

13:51.831 --> 13:53.397
PUT IT IN A NECKLACE
OR SOMETHING.

13:53.441 --> 13:56.270
OF COURSE. UH, MAY I --
MAY I SEE IT?

13:56.313 --> 13:57.706
OH, YEAH.

14:00.404 --> 14:01.928
UH,
LET ME GET MY LOUPE.

14:01.971 --> 14:03.799
WE'LL JUST NEED TO TAKE
A CLOSER LOOK AT THE STONE.

14:03.843 --> 14:05.235
EXCUSE ME, SIR.

14:05.279 --> 14:06.802
I'M HELPING ANOTHER CUSTOMER
RIGHT NOW, SIR.

14:06.846 --> 14:08.804
FBI -- GIVE THEM BACK
THEIR RING RIGHT NOW,

14:08.848 --> 14:11.241
OR I WILL BE FORCED
TO SHOOT YOU.

14:11.285 --> 14:12.460
DON'T WORRY.
JUST KIDDING.

14:12.503 --> 14:13.940
I DON'T EVEN CARRY
A REAL GUN.

14:13.983 --> 14:15.985
