THAT THIS CASE ISN'T CLOSED,

25:52.986 --> 25:55.118
IT'S LIKELY THAT
SHE'LL CANCEL THE WEDDING

25:55.162 --> 25:56.598
AND JOIN THE HUNT.

25:56.642 --> 25:59.427
YEAH, THERE'S PLENTY OF TIME
TO TELL THEM AFTER.

25:59.470 --> 26:03.300
BUT...IF HE'S STILL ALIVE,
YOU KNOW,

26:03.344 --> 26:08.131
KELLER'S UNPREDICTABLE,
AND JANE DID TRY TO KILL HIM.

26:08.175 --> 26:10.786
YOU KNOW, JUST IN CASE,

26:10.830 --> 26:13.136
WHY DON'T WE PUT SOME BODIES
AT THE WEDDING,

26:13.180 --> 26:15.138
JUST TO KEEP
AN EYE OUT.

26:15.182 --> 26:17.140
AND IT'S MY HOUSE,
SO I'LL ARRANGE IT.

26:17.184 --> 26:19.012
YOU SURE?

26:19.055 --> 26:21.014
OH, YEAH, YEAH, YEAH.
IT'S SOMETHING TO KEEP ME BUSY.

26:21.057 --> 26:22.406
OKAY, THANKS.

26:22.450 --> 26:24.757
ABBOTT SAID
IT'S TOTALLY UP TO YOU,

26:24.800 --> 26:27.760
BUT THAT YOU'D PROBABLY PREFER
TO HOLD THE CEREMONY OUTSIDE,

26:27.803 --> 26:29.762
AND THERE ISN'T REALLY
A ROOM INSIDE BIG ENOUGH.

26:29.805 --> 26:31.764
WELL, HOW MANY PEOPLE
ARE WE TALKING ABOUT?

26:31.807 --> 26:33.766
OH! A LOT OF PEOPLE
ARE TALKING ABOUT IT.

26:33.809 --> 26:36.290
WELL, WE ONLY INVITED
LIKE 15 PEOPLE.

26:36.333 --> 26:40.120
MM...MORE LIKE 25 OR --
I KNOW.

26:40.163 --> 26:41.643
AND I DON'T THINK
PEOPLE ARE WAITING FOR, LIKE,

26:41.687 --> 26:45.516
A PRINTED INVITATION...
SEEING AS THERE ISN'T ONE.

26:45.560 --> 26:48.824
BUT, HEY, O-ON THE PLUS SIDE,
YOU'RE POPULAR, GIRL!

26:48.868 --> 26:50.434
IS THAT WHAT
ALL THESE TABLES ARE FOR?

26:50.478 --> 26:52.262
YEAH, ABBOTT THOUGHT
THEY'D BE USEFUL. DON'T WORRY.

26:52.306 --> 26:54.090
HE'S COVERING
THE RENTAL...

26:54.134 --> 26:56.658
AND THE BARTENDER...
AND THE CATERER.

26:56.702 --> 26:59.269
I GUESS THEY'RE HIS
WEDDING GIFT. I DON'T KNOW.

26:59.313 --> 27:00.923
HEY, HERE'S A MENU.

27:00.967 --> 27:04.231
THERE'S A CATERER?YEAH. YEAH, IT'S FINE.

27:04.274 --> 27:06.015
ABBOTT'S LOADED.
I MEAN, LOOK AT THIS HOUSE.

27:06.059 --> 27:08.365
I THINK HIS WIFE CLEANED UP
IN THE PRIVATE SECTOR.

27:08.409 --> 27:09.540
WOW.

27:09.584 --> 27:12.674
HERE WE ARE.
HEY, EVERYBODY OUT.

27:12.718 --> 27:14.197
HEY, TERESA!
HEY!

27:14.241 --> 27:17.070
WE'RE HERE!
HEY-HEY!

27:17.113 --> 27:18.593
T!
[ LAUGHTER ]

27:18.637 --> 27:21.248
HI!
[ Chuckling ] WOW!

27:21.291 --> 27:23.903
YOU ALL CAME!
SO MANY PEOPLE.

27:23.946 --> 27:27.646
YEAH, HEY. SURE WE CAME.
WE'RE GONNA LET OUR SISTER DOWN?

27:27.689 --> 27:29.517
[ LAUGHTER ]

27:29.560 --> 27:31.737
CONGRATULATIONS.
THANKS.

27:31.780 --> 27:33.216
YEAH, HEY, GUYS, SAY HI TO YOUR
AUNT TERESA, ALL RIGHT?

27:33.260 --> 27:34.914
HI!
HI!

27:34.957 --> 27:36.393
WHO IS THIS?

27:36.437 --> 27:38.352
OH, T, THIS IS LUCY,
MY FIANCéE.
AAH!

27:38.395 --> 27:39.962
LUCY, TERESA.

27:40.006 --> 27:42.791
I AM SO FREAKED OUT
TO MEET YOU AT LAST.

27:42.835 --> 27:44.401
WE'RE GONNA BE
SISTERS! YAY!

27:44.445 --> 27:45.533
YAY!

27:45.576 --> 27:47.666
IT'S A LONG STORY.[ CHUCKLES ]

27:49.276 --> 27:51.713
SO, YOU'RE ALL HERE.
WELCOME TO AUSTIN.

27:51.757 --> 27:53.802
THANKS.YEAH, IT LOOKS LIKE WE BROUGHT
