27:53.846 --> 27:55.630
FBI! [ LAUGHS ]

27:55.674 --> 27:58.111
SORRY, I'M FREAKING OUT
RIGHT NOW. [ LAUGHS ]

27:58.154 --> 28:00.417
YEAH, WE GOT THAT.EXCUSE ME?

28:00.461 --> 28:01.897
YOU ALL CAME.

28:01.941 --> 28:04.247
YEAH. ALREADY SAID THAT, T.Jason: LET'S GO IN!

28:04.291 --> 28:07.381
JASON! JASON!
COME HERE!
YEAH!
OKAY.

28:07.424 --> 28:09.775
CONGRATULATIONS.
THANK YOU.

28:09.818 --> 28:12.168
[ CHUCKLES ]YAY.

