[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]

28:18.218 --> 28:19.088
[ SIGHS ]

28:24.615 --> 28:25.442
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

28:25.486 --> 28:27.096
UH, EXCUSE ME, SIR.

28:27.140 --> 28:29.751
WE HAVE
AN ODD COINCIDENCE...

28:29.795 --> 28:32.275
OR NOT. MAYBE.

28:32.319 --> 28:34.103
AUSTIN P.D. GOT
A MISSING-PERSON'S REPORT

28:34.147 --> 28:36.715
ON A LOCAL TELEVISION REPORTER
NAMED DAN GLOVER.

28:36.758 --> 28:38.760
THE ONE
THAT INTERVIEWED JANE.

28:38.804 --> 28:41.110
YEAH, LEFT WORK THURSDAY NIGHT,
HASN'T BEEN SEEN SINCE.

28:41.154 --> 28:43.417
THE WEIRD THING IS,
HE CALLED HERE

28:43.460 --> 28:45.245
RIGHT AROUND THE TIME HE WAS
LAST SEEN. I SPOKE TO HIM.

28:45.288 --> 28:46.899
HE SAID HE WANTED TO
INTERVIEW JANE AGAIN,

28:46.942 --> 28:48.248
AND I SAID
HE WAS UNAVAILABLE

28:48.291 --> 28:51.294
BECAUSE HE WAS
GETTING...MARRIED.

28:51.338 --> 28:54.689
SO, YOU'RE NOT EVEN SURE
IF YOU SPOKE TO GLOVER?

28:54.733 --> 28:57.692
NO, I MEAN,
I WAS CERTAIN AT THE TIME.

28:57.736 --> 29:00.303
OBVIOUSLY, IT WAS
HIS CALLER I.D., BUT NOW --

29:00.347 --> 29:02.436
SO, WE HAVE TO ASSUME
THE KILLER'S ALIVE
AND LOOKING FOR JANE.

29:02.479 --> 29:04.917
HOW MANY AGENTS ARE YOU GONNA
HAVE AT THE WEDDING?

29:04.960 --> 29:07.920
FOUR, BUT NOW I THINK
WE SHOULD PROBABLY HAVE MORE.

29:07.963 --> 29:09.530
AT LEAST 10.

29:09.573 --> 29:10.836
WE'RE GONNA NEED EYES
ON THE FRONT AND BACKYARDS

29:10.879 --> 29:12.185
AND THE SURROUNDING
NEIGHBORHOODS.

29:12.228 --> 29:13.534
WE SHOULD HAVE A CHOPPER
ON STANDBY

29:13.577 --> 29:14.578
IN CASE
WE NEED TO PURSUE.

29:14.622 --> 29:16.276
YES, SIR.

29:16.319 --> 29:19.496
BUT WOULDN'T IT BE WISER
TO JUST POSTPONE THE WEDDING?

29:19.540 --> 29:22.151
POSTPONE THE WEDDING?
WE'RE THE FBI.

29:23.196 --> 29:25.154
THERE IS THAT UPSIDE.

29:25.198 --> 29:29.680
WE CAN USE THE WEDDING
AS BAIT...KIND OF.

29:31.421 --> 29:32.771
I'M GONNA GO CHECK
ON THAT CHOPPER.

29:35.208 --> 29:37.384
STILL THINK WE SHOULDN'T TELL
JANE AND LISBON?

29:37.427 --> 29:40.387
WE'RE THE FBI.

29:40.430 --> 29:43.869
JUST LIKE YOU SAID,
WE CAN HANDLE IT.

29:45.827 --> 29:47.829
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

29:47.873 --> 29:49.526
Patrick: ABBOTT.

29:49.570 --> 29:51.528
HMM? HEY.

29:51.572 --> 29:54.488
[ TELEPHONE RINGING ]

29:54.531 --> 29:56.925
WHAT WERE YOU AND CHO AND TORK
HUDDLED ABOUT?

29:56.969 --> 29:59.841
NOTHING SPECIAL.

29:59.885 --> 30:02.191
NOTHING SPECIAL
THAT'S KEEPING YOU HERE

30:02.235 --> 30:04.019
WHEN YOU COULD BE IN PRAGUE
