IF IT WAS SOMETHING IMPORTANT.

30:15.161 --> 30:16.466
OH, YEAH, YEAH.
YEAH, OF COURSE.

30:16.510 --> 30:17.903
I-IF I THOUGHT

30:17.946 --> 30:18.904
