THAT WE COULDN'T HANDLE.

30:18.947 --> 30:20.601
AH.

30:20.644 --> 30:22.429
YOU KNOW, UM...

30:24.474 --> 30:26.781
...I'VE BEEN GETTING
SOME CALLS ABOUT YOU,

30:26.825 --> 30:28.609
AND MY BOSSES WANT TO KNOW
IF YOU'RE STICKING AROUND.

30:28.652 --> 30:29.871
THAT'S A GOOD QUESTION.

30:29.915 --> 30:32.221
MM.

30:32.265 --> 30:34.571
ALL RIGHT, WELL,
NO PRESSURE.

30:34.615 --> 30:36.878
BUT IF YOU'RE GOING,
THERE IS SOME LEGAL STUFF

30:36.922 --> 30:40.577
THAT WE NEED TO HANDLE TO
EXPUNGE THAT DEAL THAT WE MADE.

30:40.621 --> 30:43.798
THE NAPKIN?
MM-HMM. [ LAUGHS ]

30:46.322 --> 30:47.628
I'M GETTING MARRIED
TOMORROW.

30:47.671 --> 30:49.108
MM-HMM.

30:49.151 --> 30:52.938
THEN I'M BUILDING A HOUSE,
AND...BEYOND THAT,

30:52.981 --> 30:56.115
I GENUINELY HAVE NO IDEA.

30:56.158 --> 30:59.466
AND I CAN'T
DO THIS JOB FOREVER,

30:59.509 --> 31:01.424
BUT IT'S GONNA BE TOUGH
TO GIVE UP.

31:01.468 --> 31:04.079
YEAH, IT'S HARD GIVING UP
MAKING A DIFFERENCE, HUH?

31:04.123 --> 31:06.125
NO, EVERYONE
MAKES A DIFFERENCE.

31:06.168 --> 31:07.953
HARD TO GIVE UP
THE CHASE.

31:07.996 --> 31:10.651
OH, YEAH.

31:10.694 --> 31:13.306
THAT IT IS.

31:13.349 --> 31:15.830
[ CHUCKLES ]

31:15.874 --> 31:18.920
SO, YOU, UH,
LET ME KNOW WHEN YOU KNOW.

31:18.964 --> 31:21.575
I WILL.

31:21.618 --> 31:25.535
IT HAS BEEN VERY GOOD
WORKING WITH YOU, PATRICK.

31:25.579 --> 31:27.015
YOU TOO, DENNIS.

31:27.059 --> 31:29.713
I REALLY APPRECIATE
YOUR HONESTY.

31:29.757 --> 31:31.063
I LOVE YOU FOR THAT.

31:32.542 --> 31:34.980
THANK YOU.

31:40.986 --> 31:42.422
[ SIGHS ]

31:42.465 --> 31:44.424
OKAY, YOU GOT ME.
I WAS LYING.

31:44.467 --> 31:48.254
THERE IS SOMETHING
I NEED TO TALK TO YOU ABOUT.

31:57.089 --> 31:58.829
[ SIGHS ]

32:01.093 --> 32:02.921
[ SNIFFLES ]

32:02.964 --> 32:04.923
HEY.
HI.

32:04.966 --> 32:06.968
NICE FLOWERS.

32:07.012 --> 32:10.624
MM.
THEY'RE CENTERPIECES.

32:10.667 --> 32:12.060
IT'S A SYLVAN THEME.

32:12.104 --> 32:15.629
SYLVAN THEME.
ALL RIGHT. COOL, I GUESS.

32:15.672 --> 32:19.981
HOW MANY...PEOPLE ARE
ACTUALLY COMING TO THIS THING?

32:20.025 --> 32:24.290
NOBODY KNOWS EXACTLY.
[ SIGHS ]

32:24.333 --> 32:25.987
OKAY.

32:26.031 --> 32:29.817
[ Crying ] HOW DID THIS HAPPEN?
THIS IS NOT WHAT I WANTED.

32:29.860 --> 32:31.950
[ SIGHS DEEPLY ]

32:31.993 --> 32:33.299
WELL, I LIKE
THE SYLVAN THEME.

32:33.342 --> 32:36.041
WE SHOULD HAVE JUST
ELOPED LIKE YOU SAID.

32:36.084 --> 32:38.217
WHAT ABOUT YOUR FAMILY?

32:38.260 --> 32:40.001
OH, THEY WOULDN'T CARE.
I JUST TALKED TO THEM
AT THE HOTEL.

32:40.045 --> 32:41.481
THEY FOUND A MINIBAR.

32:41.524 --> 32:43.831
THEY'RE LIKE CAVEMEN
ARGUING OVER A DEAD ANTELOPE.

32:43.874 --> 32:48.836
ALL RIGHT, WELL, UH...
LET'S RUN, HUH?

32:48.879 --> 32:51.839
WE'LL TELL NOBODY,
JUST THE JUDGE.

32:51.882 --> 32:53.667
I'LL HAVE HER MEET US
AT OUR LITTLE CABIN

32:53.710 --> 32:54.755
TOMORROW MORNING.

32:54.798 --> 32:56.061
THE CABIN?

32:56.104 --> 32:57.584
JUST US.

32:57.627 --> 32:58.846
WHAT, YOU THINK
THE JUDGE WOULD DO THAT?

32:58.889 --> 33:00.456
WELL, SURE.

33:00.500 --> 33:01.980
I MEAN, SHE'S DRIVING IN
FROM SAN ANTONIO TONIGHT.

33:02.023 --> 33:03.459
CHANGE OF VENUE MAKES
NO DIFFERENCE TO HER.

33:03.503 --> 33:05.157
WELL,
WHAT ABOUT THE WITNESSES?

33:05.200 --> 33:07.507
WE'LL GET SOMEONE,
A PARK RANGER.

33:07.550 --> 33:08.856
[ CHUCKLES ]

33:08.899 --> 33:09.944
YOU KNOW WHAT?
LET'S DO IT.
YEAH.

33:09.988 --> 33:11.337
IT'S OUR LIFE, DAMN IT.
YES.

33:11.380 --> 33:12.903
I LOVE YOU. THANK YOU.I LOVE YOU, TOO.

33:12.947 --> 33:14.166
HEY, THERE'S A --I'M GONNA GO GET MY DRESS,

33:14.209 --> 33:15.210
AND I'M GONNA GO
TO THE AIRSTREAM.

33:15.254 --> 33:16.603
I'LL MEET YOU THERE.

33:16.646 --> 33:17.996
WELL, THERE'S ANOTHER
VERY GOOD REASON

33:18.039 --> 33:19.823
WHY WE SHOULD ELOPE,
ALL RIGHT?

33:19.867 --> 33:22.000
KELLER IS APPARENTLY
STILL ALIVE,

33:22.043 --> 33:24.132
AND HE'S MAD AT ME
FOR SOME REASON.

33:24.176 --> 33:25.916
OH, MY GOD.

33:25.960 --> 33:29.398
YEAH, SO CHO AND HIS PEOPLE
ARE GONNA STAKE OUT THIS HOUSE.

33:29.442 --> 33:31.270
WHEN KELLER SHOWS UP,
THEY'LL NAB HIM.

33:31.313 --> 33:33.446
YOU WERE GONNA WITHHOLD
THIS INFORMATION FROM ME?
HUH?

33:33.489 --> 33:35.578
