33:40.366 --> 33:42.150
I AGREE WITH YOU 100%.
OKAY.

33:42.194 --> 33:44.674
HONESTY.I AM GONNA GO...
GET MY DRESS.

33:44.718 --> 33:46.589
FIRE UP THE AIRSTREAM.YOU GO, GIRL.

33:52.204 --> 33:54.684
HI. JUDGE HAMILTON,
PATRICK JANE.

33:54.728 --> 33:57.513
UH, THERE'S BEEN
A CHANGE OF VENUE.

33:57.557 --> 34:00.516
OKAY.
NO PROBLEM, MR. JANE.

34:00.560 --> 34:02.040
