THE EXACT ADDRESS

34:02.083 --> 34:04.042
AND PERHAPS
A DECENT MOTEL NEARBY.

34:04.085 --> 34:05.869
I'LL SEE YOU TOMORROW.

34:05.913 --> 34:07.958
GREAT. BYE.

34:16.445 --> 34:18.099
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

34:18.143 --> 34:20.014
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

34:43.472 --> 34:44.647
