34:46.823 --> 34:48.434
FIVE DRESSED AS CATERING
AND VALET SERVICE,

34:48.477 --> 34:50.131
SIX ON THE PERIMETER,

34:50.175 --> 34:52.307
AND SIX UNDERCOVER MOBILES
COVERING THE APPROACH ROADS.

34:52.351 --> 34:53.874
WHEN THE GUESTS
GET HERE,

34:53.917 --> 34:55.832
I'LL GATHER THEM INSIDE
AND EXPLAIN THE SITUATION.

34:55.876 --> 34:57.138
MOST OF THEM
ARE LAW ENFORCEMENT,

34:57.182 --> 34:58.705
SO THEY'LL UNDERSTAND.

34:58.748 --> 35:00.663
WHAT IS IT, WYLIE?

35:00.707 --> 35:02.361
OFFICE GOT A CALL OFF THE BOLO
FROM A CLERK

35:02.404 --> 35:03.884
AT THE SOUTH AUSTIN
REGISTRY OFFICE.

35:03.927 --> 35:06.539
A MAN WITH EXTENSIVE BURNS
CAME IN YESTERDAY

35:06.582 --> 35:07.888
AND PRETENDED TO FILL OUT
A FORM.

35:07.931 --> 35:09.368
THE CLERK THINKS
HE MAY HAVE TAKEN A PEEK

35:09.411 --> 35:11.718
AT THE MARRIAGE-LICENSE FORMS
ON HER DESK.

35:11.761 --> 35:14.068
SO THAT CONFIRMS IT.
HE ISCOMING TO THE WEDDING.

35:14.112 --> 35:16.026
WELL, WE GOT IT COVERED.
WHY ARE YOU SO ANXIOUS, WYLIE?

35:16.070 --> 35:18.420
I KNOW ALL THE STATE FORMS FROM
WHEN I USED TO WORK DOWNTOWN.

35:18.464 --> 35:20.248
THE MARRIAGE-LICENSE FORM
DOESN'T ASK

35:20.292 --> 35:21.554
WHERE THE WEDDING IS.

35:21.597 --> 35:23.164
IT JUST ASKS
WHO THE OFFICIANT IS.

35:23.208 --> 35:24.165
WELL,
THAT'S THE JUDGE.

35:24.209 --> 35:25.862
YEAH.

35:26.689 --> 35:28.735
[ DUCKS QUACKING ]

35:36.221 --> 35:39.963
[ BREATHES DEEPLY ]

36:04.988 --> 36:06.773
HEY, YOU.

36:06.816 --> 36:08.209
Patrick: HI.

36:14.868 --> 36:17.000
WOW.

36:17.044 --> 36:22.832
WELL, NO MATTER WHAT HAPPENS,
FROM THIS POINT ON,

36:22.876 --> 36:26.836
WE HAVE TO PROMISE EACH OTHER
THAT WE WILL ALWAYS

36:26.880 --> 36:27.924
LOOK ON
THE BRIGHT SIDE.

36:27.968 --> 36:30.318
I PROMISE.

36:32.233 --> 36:34.235
ME TOO.

37:09.183 --> 37:11.229
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ][ GUN COCKS ]

37:20.586 --> 37:22.109
FREEZE!
DROP THE GUN!

37:22.152 --> 37:23.284
