WHEN YOU'RE HONEST
WITH ME?

37:35.427 --> 37:37.080
Thank you.

37:37.124 --> 37:38.734
LET'S DO THIS.

37:38.778 --> 37:40.301
NO HARD FEELINGS.

37:44.610 --> 37:45.567
[ SIGHS ]

