AND, YOU, TERESA,
DO YOU TAKE PATRICK

38:04.891 --> 38:06.849
TO BE YOUR LAWFUL,
WEDDED HUSBAND,

38:06.893 --> 38:09.635
TO HAVE AND TO HOLD
IN SICKNESS AND HEALTH,

38:09.678 --> 38:12.986
FOR BETTER OR FOR WORSE,
TILL DEATH DO YOU PART?

38:13.029 --> 38:14.814
I DO.

38:14.857 --> 38:17.947
THEN BY THE POWER GRANTED ME
BY THE STATE OF TEXAS,

38:17.991 --> 38:21.255
I DECLARE YOU HUSBAND
AND WIFE.

38:21.299 --> 38:24.563
YOU MAY KISS THE BRIDE.

38:27.783 --> 38:30.220
[ CHEERS AND APPLAUSE ]

38:30.264 --> 38:35.791
LADIES AND GENTLEMEN,
PATRICK AND TERESA.

